snippet.title: FILCHER trailer
snippet.description:
Filcher is a first-person 2.5D noir stealth game. As Sporey the master thief, infiltrate guarded buildings to steal from the wealthy and corrupt, using only your senses, your wits, and a handful of tools and gadgets. http://filchergame.com

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1355650/Filcher/
Itch.io: https://johan-hjarpe.itch.io/filcher

My website: https://johanhjarpe.com
MythoLogic Interactive website: https://mythologicinteractive.com
